'''Nostalgia Industry''' is the [[monetization]] of humans' natural [[wikt:tendency|tendencies]] to wish to relive and enhance [[nostalgia|fond memories]]. Classic examples of this are the tendencies of [[colleges]] and [[universities]] (and approved license-holders) to sell [[memorabilia]] and other items to [[alumni]] and their family in an effort to help recapture memories and recruit the next generation of alumni.

